" lang=\"DE\">&nbsp; Schrift, einheitliches Design, keine Knicke oder Flecken...)</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:de\"=\"\" lang=\"DE\">- inhaltlich schlüssig und überzeugend (z.B. auf Aspekte der </span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:de\"=\"\" lang=\"DE\">&nbsp; Stellenanzeige eingehen, begründen warum man gut auf die</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:de\"=\"\" lang=\"DE\">&nbsp; Stelle passt...)</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:de\"=\"\" lang=\"DE\">- und vieles mehr...</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:de\"=\"\" lang=\"DE\"><br></span></li></ul><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:de\"=\"\" lang=\"DE\">Bevor du eine Bewerbung abschickst, solltest du daher am besten mindestens eine Person Korrektur lesen lassen, um unnötige Fehler zu vermeiden.<br></span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:de\"=\"\" lang=\"DE\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:de\"=\"\" lang=\"DE\">Leider hat \"Maria Hali\" ihre Bewerbung etwas zu schnell abgeschickt und einige Fehler übersehen. <br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:de\"=\"\" lang=\"DE\">Sieh dir ihren Lebenslauf und ihr Anschreiben genau an und markiere die Fehler, die dir auffallen in rot. Deine Bemerkungen kannst du in das Arbeitsblatt E4a eintragen.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:de\"=\"\" lang=\"DE\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:de\"=\"\" lang=\"DE\">Lade anschließend die korrigierte Bewerbung sowie das Arbeitsblatt hoch.<br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:de\"=\"\" lang=\"DE\"><br></span></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"width: 499.25px; height: 333.143px;\" src=\"../../upload/files/201711205.jpg		\"></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:de\"=\"\" lang=\"DE\"><br></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><br><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:de\"=\"\" lang=\"DE\"></span></p>\n\n                                   