idi-font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;That other ceases to pay its debts or becomes\nunable to pay its debts within the meaning of any Insolvency law in force in\nGhana. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;tab-stops:1.0in\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n-.25in;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\" century=\"\" gothic\"\"=\"\">6.4<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;That other disposes of the whole or any\nsubstantial part of its undertaking or assets or;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;tab-stops:1.0in\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n-.25in;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\" century=\"\" gothic\"\"=\"\">6.5<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;That other ceases or threatens to cease to\ncarry on all or any substantial part of its business.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;tab-stops:1.0in\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoN